      "description": "## Native PDF Ink 0.1.0\n\nInitial release.\n\n- Handwrite on Obsidian PDFs (pen, graphite pencil, eraser, lasso)\n- Vault sidecars + autosave/recovery; original PDFs unchanged; export annotated PDF\n- Draw mode opt-in; zoom-friendly ink compositing\n\n### Install\n\nCopy `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` into `<Vault>/.obsidian/plugins/obsidian-native-pdf-ink/`, reload Obsidian, enable the plugin.",
